#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "In this module you can change &kde; default components."
msgid "In this module, you can change &kde; default components."
msgstr "I denne modulen kan du endre &kde;s standardkomponenter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Components are programs that handle basic tasks, like the terminal "
#| "emulator, the text editor and the email client. Different &kde; "
#| "applications sometimes need to invoke a console emulator, send a mail or "
#| "display some text."
msgid ""
"Components are programs that handle basic tasks, like the web browser, "
"terminal emulator, the file manager, the email client, the electronic map, "
"and the dialer. Different &kde; applications sometimes need to invoke a "
"console emulator, send an email, manage files and folders, show the map or "
"dial a number on your phone."
msgstr ""
"Komponenter er programmer som tar seg av grunnleggende oppgaver, slik som "
"terminalemulator, tekstredigering og e-postklient. Forskjellige &kde;-"
"programmer trenger av og til å kalle på en konsollemulator, sende en e-post "
"eller vise litt tekst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do so consistently, these applications always call the same components. "
"Here you can select which programs these components are."
msgstr ""
"Disse programmene kaller alltid opp de samme komponentene, for å være "
"konsekvente. Her kan du velge hvilke programmer disse komponentene er."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
